column5: that truly does help, I do this all the time
I live in India so I guess it sucks that there won't be a show in any of the Indian cities. I literally would have given anything just to go to a show if it was here.
I know the feeling. I'm a huge disappointment myself. I know how it feels when you fail and everything comes crumbling down and your parents think it's because you didn't study, you failed
